# Responsive Design System

## Breakpoints

| Tier | Width | Grid | Behavior |
|------|-------|------|----------|
| Phone | <600px | 2 col | Compact, bottom sheet |
| Large Phone | 600-767px | 3 col | Bottom sheet |
| Tablet | 768-1023px | 4 col | Bottom sheet |  
| Desktop | ≥1024px | 7 col | Inline food container |

## Guidelines

1. **Mobile-first**: Base styles target phones, then scale up
2. **Bottom sheet vs inline**: Desktop (≥1024px) uses inline food container; all smaller sizes use bottom sheet modal
3. **Touch targets**: Minimum 32px on phone, 44px on desktop
4. **Test all tiers**: Always verify layouts at 375px, 600px, 768px, 1024px

## CSS Classes

- `.desktop-only` - Hidden on mobile/tablet (<1024px)
- `.days-grid` - Main grid container, column count varies by breakpoint
- `.day-card` - Individual day cards, sizing scales per tier
